title: The Swiftmas Song Parody Battle
description:
We are going to throw it back on this Taylor Tuesday.. Last year, the office Swifties battled it out for a Christmas card from Taylor Swift herself. The challenge was to perform a song parody. Who was crowned the winner and got the coveted autographed card? And listening to this now, which song is your fav?
What would you like from us? Let us know! There are lots of ways to contact us!
